TITLE: Referencing userVariables in TestCafe Tests
DESCRIPTION: This JavaScript snippet shows how to use custom user variables defined in the configuration file. It imports the `userVariables` object from the `testcafe` module and uses a variable, 'url', to set the page under test. Dependencies: TestCafe and a configuration file with `userVariables` defined.
