SOURCE: https://github.com/devexpress/testcafe/blob/master/test/functional/fixtures/api/raw/upload/test-data/test2.txt#_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: HTML
CODE:
```
<input type="button" value="Click me" id="button1" onclick="window.firstButtonClicked = true">
```

